msgctxt "96"
msgid "Say, did you realize there's a \"Sky Finance\" in that\r\n"
"building there?"
msgstr "Dime, ¿sabías que hay un \"Sky Finance\" en ese\r\n"
"edificio de allí?"

msgctxt "1588"
msgid "Familiar Host"
msgstr "Hostess Conocido"

msgctxt "1592"
msgid "Talk_Info_R"
msgstr "Talk_Info_R"

msgctxt "1596"
msgid "Akiyama"
msgstr "Akiyama"

msgctxt "1600"
msgid "Talk_No"
msgstr "Talk_No"

msgctxt "84_Familiar Host"
msgid "Hey there, Akiyama-san."
msgstr "Buenas, Akiyama-san."

msgctxt "108_Akiyama"
msgid "That's actually why I'm here."
msgstr "De hecho, por eso estoy aquí."

msgctxt "120_Familiar Host"
msgid "Guy's gotta be out of his mind. He must not realize what\r\n"
"he's in for, trying a stupid stunt like that."
msgstr "Ha de ser un loco de remate. No debe saber en lo\r\n"
"que se está metiendo, intentando una estúpida estafa como esa."

msgctxt "132_Akiyama"
msgid "Oh, come on, now. I wouldn't do anything all that terrible,\r\n"
"would I?"
msgstr "Oh, vamos. No le haría algo tan terrible,\r\n"
"¿tú crees?"

msgctxt "144_Familiar Host"
msgid "Sometimes I wonder..."
msgstr "A veces me lo pregunto..."

msgctxt "156_Familiar Host"
msgid "Do you know where you're headed? That building on the corner\r\n"
"there."
msgstr "¿Sabes donde está? Es el edificio en el rincón\r\n"
"de allí."

msgctxt "168_Akiyama"
msgid "Okay. Thanks."
msgstr "Vale, Gracias."

